Detect AdBlock and show a customizable popup to politely request users to disable their ad blocker.

== Description ==

AdBlock Detector Popup helps you recover lost ad revenue by detecting AdBlock and showing a customizable popup.

**Features:**
- Detects uBlock Origin, AdBlock Plus, and similar
- Custom popup title, message, and button text
- Admin option to enable/disable popup
- Popup shown only once per session
- Fully responsive and lightweight

== Installation ==

1. Upload `adblock-detector-popup` folder to `/wp-content/plugins/`
2. Activate the plugin from **Plugins** menu
3. Go to **Settings > AdBlock Detector** to configure

